I know everyone always says the Halo thing but it really is that good. Sure it gets repetitive at times and the indoor environments don't vary all the much at times but the good totally overrides the bad.<br>
<br>
That said Jet Set Radio Future, Oddworld, Hunter, Quantum Redshift and even Buffy are all great games too. My main complaint is that Soulcalibur 2 has yet to surface. Soulcalibur still pisses all over any other fighting game.<br>
<br>
